{"tid":1954761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搵到500人 立法會多一席！","createTime":"2020-04-02T04:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T06:08:28.000Z","uid":101392,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a772997f22050b0d812ac12236a1ce8101f3742e","tid":1954761,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:58:52.000Z","msg":"區諾軒：【功能組別 - 終極之戰】最後一個月，召喚所有BR人士搶攻<br />\n<br />\n坦白講，我行左近10年政治路，不得不承認，谷hit rate真係弱項。<br />\n<br />\n呢段時間我嘗試喺Facebook、YouTube、傳媒等等唔同嘅平台講功能組別嘅戰線，反應都未如理想，YouTube仲要得300個人sub，坦白講。我覺得自己真係做得好差。<br />\n<br />\n要立法會過半，戰勝功能組別是必要條件，真係唯一識得做嘅，係繼續宣揚相信正確嘅事。距離選民登記只有最後一個月，「出版界」同「進出口界」係最後有機會嘅突圍嘅缺口。點解？唔使你入商會一年，仲有，都係當你登記新公司票，搏5月2號新登記截止最後一水。<br />\n<br />\n只要你有張登記超過一年嘅BR，而又無用公司喺其他功能組別登記過團體票，你都可以喺嚟緊9月立法會有票選功能組別！<br />\n<br />\n暴政最想見到就係人民嘅怠慢，懶於監察，懶於行動，懶於反抗，咁就正中極權下懷。希望大家把握最後一個月推爆佢，做好自己崗位嘅宣傳！我哋先至對得住好多喺呢大半年犧牲左嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n進出口Whatapps熱線：68461562<br />\n體演文出Whatapps熱線：66700860<br />\n<br />\n#倒數一個月 #寸土必爭 #立會過半<br />\n----<br />\n🎥【Youtube 頻道】<a href=\"http://bit.ly/anhyoutube\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fanhyoutube&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=e699ce31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/anhyoutube</a><br />\n📣【Telegram】<a href=\"http://t.me/aunokhin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Faunokhin&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=c2365748\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/aunokhin</a><br />\n🐦【Twitter】<a href=\"http://twitter.com/loktinau\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Floktinau&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=81a2c38b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/loktinau</a>"},{"pid":"a2d909156c0cdd16ab14e027656c2235a02f5b20","tid":1954761,"uid":101392,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p04LpnG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp04LpnG.jpg&h=326578bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W9XMTf5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW9XMTf5.jpg&h=e294c95d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xTqOm9v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxTqOm9v.jpg&h=735005a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dc0bjWe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDc0bjWe.jpg&h=eafe7586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vu97CHX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvu97CHX.jpg&h=fe1d2479&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e15e782231e031460b5ce26c683dccda369428bd","tid":1954761,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:00:31.000Z","msg":"br？"},{"pid":"97633b5f7e4ee34f5de816dd8064ce670a0fe4e9","tid":1954761,"uid":39503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:00:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"feccac9b7b170144aa147b1670efa38b82bf5b48","tid":1954761,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e15e782231e031460b5ce26c683dccda369428bd","tid":1954761,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:00:31.000Z","msg":"br？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:01:44.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n要搵到500位有滿一年商業登記嘅手足"},{"pid":"1c4e825b39498135272b5a10c386b7c97a972785","tid":1954761,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:02:28.000Z","msg":"原來可以咁樣幫還押手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1954173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1954173</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e03d79806acdfa960409634bac2c1cc57cdfd083","tid":1954761,"uid":181747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:02:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6a06b18b05090f8c47f3e0b59f9fd83a6e918b7","tid":1954761,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:03:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f93205a18863eb4a9cc47eb285ae9f94677bb78","tid":1954761,"uid":306618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:03:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fdbab06b5f07fbc77f07ff14ec936a59d96782f","tid":1954761,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:03:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85cb40363e21d24728eb950a644c22dc213e8d83","tid":1954761,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:03:47.000Z","msg":"補link：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/581689778588087/posts/2792074844216225/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F581689778588087%2Fposts%2F2792074844216225%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=e4579e1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/581689778588087/posts/2792074844216225/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"8343f156054c5531f0b780829e5e21ade7efcc3a","tid":1954761,"uid":101392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:06:49.000Z","msg":"上屆<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elections.gov.hk/legco2016/chi/rs_fc_V.html?1585803923361\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.gov.hk%2Flegco2016%2Fchi%2Frs_fc_V.html%3F1585803923361&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=bc27d320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elections.gov.hk/legco2016/chi/rs_fc_V.html?1585803923361</a><br />\n體育演藝文化出版界<br />\n周博賢 809<br />\n馬逢國 1389"},{"pid":"3734cf0adc9e9657836c7742d6ea24b1c30b065b","tid":1954761,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:11:17.000Z","msg":"help push"},{"pid":"7f4b3ff1d07236218fbd9d8c5cab82b9a4de5c1f","tid":1954761,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:12:28.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"6324adbc678cc70f0db957547d4feb3c07944d98","tid":1954761,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:17:52.000Z","msg":"區軒示範咗 出版《區諾軒的離別感言》<br />\n<br />\n/在民主派「議會過半」的號角聲下，多個界別正積極爭取新選民登記，希望突破重圍，其中較少人留意的體育、演藝、文化及出版界也成為民主派搶灘目標。正準備登記為「出版小組」選民的前立法會議員區諾軒透露，市民只要將旗下一間註冊公司的業務更改為「出版」，然後再以該公司名義出版一份簡單刊物，再向報刊註冊處登記，便合資格登記，以沖淡由紅色資本「三中商」盤踞的出版小組，強調功能組別制度「荒謬」，民主派須「搵位」突圍，拉建制派下馬。<br />\n<br />\n上屆立法會選舉，建制派馬逢國以580票之差擊敗民主派周博賢，奪體育、演藝、文化及出版界議席，周博賢大幅收窄以往民主派與建制派的差距，故民主派搶灘此界別非零希望。根據區諾軒所指，要成為此界別中的出版小組選民絕不困難，指多年前有記者以影印機複製10多份刊物後派發，便透過一間註冊公司成功登記為出版小組選民。<br />\n<br />\n擁有一間註冊公司的區諾軒也正嘗試登記：「我係同出版界毫無關係，但係功能組別真係好荒謬，就算你同個界別毫無關係，只要理論上合乎政府嘅登記資格，你都可以登記嗰個界別嘅選民，出版界就係其中一個我哋搵到窿路嘅界別。」<br />\n<br />\n區諾軒指，按照選舉事務處的規定，有意成為出版小組的市民，<span style=\"color: red;\">若有一間註冊公司在手，可向公司註冊處更改業務性質，稱與「出版」有關，然後製作一份簡單刊物，再向報刊註冊處登記，繳付約1,000元牌費後便有資格登記為此組別選民。他正以《區諾軒的離別感言》向報刊註冊處登記為此組別選民，現未知能否成功登記：「我真係喺街派過《區諾軒的離別感言》，我咪登記做出版小組嘅選民囉&hellip;&hellip;所以係一件好容易嘅事，（反修例的）文宣組都可以有份註冊報刊</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n不是界別一分子，卻登記為界別選民，會否落人口實？區諾軒指建制派其實也在用同一伎倆，所以民主派要奮力登記，在制度中「搵位」突圍：「功能組別唔係為界別利益，係扭曲香港市民意願嘅制度，要克服呢個制度，就係唔關事嘅人都走去登記（做選民），將呢個制度廢咗佢，令個政權唔能夠用呢個邏輯去管治⋯⋯我哋知道政改無期，所以要玩爛個制度佢，你要攬炒，就係要功能組別運作唔到。」<br />\n<br />\n他指，根正苗紅的「三中商」書商麾下多間子公司也肯定奮力動員登記為出版小組選民，力保建制派議席不失，所以民主派絕不能放棄這個戰場，尤其是公民社會經常出版不少民間刊物，這些「報刊」也應透過成立一間公司、再向報刊註冊處登記，爭取成為選民，在今屆立選踢走建制派。<br />\n<br />\n體育、演藝、文化及出版界向來包括四個小組，四個組別選民資格各異，但主要以團體選民為主，議席向由建制派奪得。更改選民資格的限期為4月2日，新選民登記截止日期則為5月2日，區諾軒呼籲合資格者盡快登記為出版小組新選民。/"},{"pid":"69b824daa98591593453b1e602ce1e2b8ea2c68f","tid":1954761,"uid":109408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:18:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9216ba496ef68d98d40ae641c776dcb2ccdb60b7","tid":1954761,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:18:26.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"0b75ae1d964b5fc480ff477cc1f40e9bc4772902","tid":1954761,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:18:36.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"45ca4439747ab03c92fb643061e8ddb086847f2d","tid":1954761,"uid":51924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,